text: Moominiiney tama yahuud kee Nasaarak nanu Yallaa kee Qhuraanak nel obtem Nummasneh Nabii Ibraahimiiy Nabii Ismaaqil kee Nabii Iscaaqhaay Nabii Yaq-qhuub kee Nabii Yaq-qhuub Samadak (raddik) Ambiya yekke maral obtem Nummasneh, Nabii Muusaa kee Nabii Qiisah tontocowwime kitoobaa (tawraat kee injiil kinnuk) kee Ambiyah inkih ken Rabbik wacyik keenih tontocowwimem Nummasneh, nanu iimaanal Ambiyak numtin fan mabaxisna yahuud kee Nasaara kah Abte innah, nanu kaa inkittoysaah kaah yaqunxee marah Anuk ixxica
